            // if we start at x=i and perform the sequence (step_add, step_sub) repeatedly.

            // This means dp_val[i] is the total y and dp_next_x[i] is the final x
            // if we start at x=i and perform step_add, then step_sub, then step_add, etc.
            // The value a[i] is used for the first step_add.
